name: V.S. WHITTY FULL WEEK EDITION
description:
A mod for friday night funkin'.

While strolling with your Girlfriend though an alleyway, you happen to notice an ominous glow coming from around the corner. Out steps Whitmore (Whitty), a hot-headed rock star who happens to have some beef with your Girlfriends parents. Think you've got what it takes to get him outta there?Please go and support the artist and composer of the music here: https://www.instagram.com/sock.clip/
